The evidence with the title 'Obama's final numbers - factcheck.org ' says Sep 29, 2017  ... For simplicity , we've combined the administrations of Democrats John F. Kennedy and his successor , Lyndon B. Johnson (who took office after Kennedy was assassinated ) , and of Republicans ... In fact , the 5.3 percent gain under Obama barely made up for the 4.2 percent loss under his predecessor . 
